{
  "name": "claude-code",
  "description": "Claude Code (Anthropic) — CLAUDE.md instructions + .claude/settings.json PostToolUse + Stop hooks. Hook commands use $CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR for cwd-stable resolution (closes #18).",
